stories.title: Cross, Macleod lead Scotland to thumping win
stories.subTitle: Scotland v UAE, World Cup Qualifier, Super Six, Bulawayo
stories.seoTitle: Cross, Macleod lead Scotland to thumping win
stories.summary: The second-wicket pair added 161 to propel Scotland to 322 for 6, their fourth-highest ODI total, which ended up proving well beyond UAE's reach
stories.byline: The Report by Liam Brickhill in Bulawayo
